Very cool...looked like it missed the lure and sliced the line with it's fangs!

Nice to see that some guys are still using Canadian Wigglers.  They are still awesome.  Their erratic swimming motion still puts them at the top of my arsenal for walleye and pike.  I've been using Canadian Wigglers for well over 40 years.
